{"tid":1550511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足可唔可以應承我，自己手足自己救？","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:44.000Z","uid":40121,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8c6c02109bfc99db30035cf87f52707ec96040","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以記住<br />\n啲狗可以咁撚惡<br />\n就係因為睇死我地係奉公守法嘅好巿民<br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知 我地睇住唔敢沖而失去嘅手足<br />\n一陣就會係狗屋度為我地嘅懦弱付出代價<br />\n軍裝無乜甲人唔多嘅話我地係咪可以試吓救人？<br />\n而家打人嘅係狗 唔可以報警等狗救<br />\n我地嘅香港 我地嘅手足 係要自己救架！<br />\n<br />\n我知大家驚 我都好驚 真係好驚！<br />\n但係七一立會我地有勇氣入去帶住手足齊上齊落<br />\n點解今日我地做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以係度應承我 最最起碼<br />\n下次狗唔係咁多 裝備唔係咁好嘅狗<br />\n試下大叫一聲打狗救人<br />\n腳震都好<br />\n陪我踏出一步去救手足<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以應承我 唔好再乞求人嘅可憐同幫助<br />\n自己手足 自己同路人 自己救啊！<br />\n<br />\n求大家應承我啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596408f61bed31a7327eca610af5ebcfbbb5f2c7","tid":1550511,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43abe00b4c9ebc8e8f2118171103dbdc2edc5b0c","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"應承我啊各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ffde9353d81565d2f72ab4d4e8f83ec34c20f6","tid":1550511,"uid":126214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"好！ 大家齊心救人 一定得 但唔好怯到走哂 會令到更多人被捕 香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10235f97a61ecd875aa3050d9ec08f376ccf55d2","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"自己手足自己救"},{"pid":"679e6236c55443bb38564f2064fb9dda0173b987","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ffde9353d81565d2f72ab4d4e8f83ec34c20f6","tid":1550511,"uid":126214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"好！ 大家齊心救人 一定得 但唔好怯到走哂 會令到更多人被捕 香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"多謝你啊手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06980a150b4a158743ab7c9bc86ddb84a42ed0c","tid":1550511,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"9月8點應對外國記者+資料整合+3首歌歌詞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550402\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550402</a>"},{"pid":"b58cb629d7328a341070131f5cf45d8c42658054","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"