s last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"4b7df3fe87a58d440a1b788509a5981fe4ec9578","tid":1550511,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa0f3c72c9672d844a5c667514f90de869692f1","tid":1550511,"uid":126214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fd8b132acb32199b55efcfdb6b86dc8f51e31d2","tid":1550511,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"有冇救人口號，叫叫下大家就潛移默化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"打狗救人！齊上齊落！衝啊"},{"pid":"a281b5fdf7b835c2444a0fadd29de0ffb795bcde","tid":1550511,"uid":264387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救人,做完嘢即走!!!!!!!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sT2nViS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A